 S_{n,k}=\sum_{i=0}^k\frac{k!(n-i)!}{n!(k-i)!}=1+\frac{k}n+\frac{k(k-1)}{n(n-1)}+\cdots+\frac{k!}{n(n-1)\cdots(n-k+1)}. 
